{"title":"[django快速上手(5/6)] 將API資料顯示到網站","uid":"7c57646176f1bc9f73cc2f7c30760f64","slug":"Computer/python/django/0005_將API資料顯示到網站","date":"2023-01-31T16:49:36.000Z","updated":"2023-02-09T16:26:39.565Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Computer/python/django/0005_將API資料顯示到網站.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://miro.medium.com/max/1200/1*slHeZngyeUr7ypEz7MNL5w.png","content":"<h1 id=\"將API資料顯示到網站\"><a href=\"#將API資料顯示到網站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"將API資料顯示到網站\"></a>將API資料顯示到網站</h1><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.github.com/users?since=0\">Github API</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"1-把API資訊導入\"><a href=\"#1-把API資訊導入\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 把API資訊導入\"></a>1. 把API資訊導入</h2><ul>\n<li>首先我們先從pizzawu中的 view.py，我們要加入API的資訊</li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">from django.shortcuts import render\n\n# Create your views here.\n\ndef home(request):\n\n    import requests\n    import json\n\n    api_request &#x3D; requests.get(&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;api.github.com&#x2F;users?since&#x3D;0&quot;)\n    api &#x3D; json.loads(api_request.content) #因為要裡面的內容，所以content\n\n\n    return render(request,&#39;home.html&#39;,&#123;&quot;api&quot;:api&#125;) # 給他key為api\n</code></pre>\n\n\n<h2 id=\"2-導入後要再HTML顯示\"><a href=\"#2-導入後要再HTML顯示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 導入後要再HTML顯示\"></a>2. 導入後要再HTML顯示</h2><ul>\n<li>修改home.html<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&#123;% extends &#39;base.html&#39;%&#125;\n\n&#123;% block content2 %&#125;\n&lt;h1&gt;Hello,I&#39;m pizza.&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;\n&lt;h2&gt;測試你看不看的到!!!!!!!!&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;\n\n&lt;p&gt;&#123;&#123;api&#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n\n\n&#123;% endblock %&#125;\n</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/a0/8b/GQ6jawCk_o.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"3-用Bootstrap美化\"><a href=\"#3-用Bootstrap美化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 用Bootstrap美化\"></a>3. 用Bootstrap美化</h2><h3 id=\"整理一下json\"><a href=\"#整理一下json\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"整理一下json\"></a>整理一下json</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&#123;% extends &#39;base.html&#39;%&#125;\n\n&#123;% block content2 %&#125;\n    &lt;h1&gt;Github List&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;\n\n    &lt;ul&gt;\n    &#123;% for i in api %&#125;\n        &lt;li&gt;&#123;&#123;i&#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;\n\n    &#123;% endfor %&#125;\n    &lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;\n\n&#123;% endblock %&#125;\n</code></pre>\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/58/66/a8MBFAfe_o.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"增加Bootstrap\"><a href=\"#增加Bootstrap\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"增加Bootstrap\"></a>增加Bootstrap</h3><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/components/card/\">https://getbootstrap.com/docs/4.4/components/card/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-markup\" data-language=\"markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">&#123;% extends &#39;base.html&#39;%&#125;\n&#123;% block content2 %&#125;\n&lt;h1&gt;Github List&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;\n&lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;row&quot;&gt;\n        &#123;% for i in api %&#125;\n        &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n        &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;col-sm&quot;&gt;\n            &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card&quot; style&#x3D;&quot;width: 18rem;&quot;&gt;\n                &lt;img src&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123;i.avatar_url&#125;&#125;&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;card-img-top&quot; alt&#x3D;&quot;Card image cap&quot;&gt;\n                &lt;div class&#x3D;&quot;card-body&quot;&gt;\n                    &lt;h5 class&#x3D;&quot;card-title&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123;i.login&#125;&#125;&lt;&#x2F;h5&gt;\n                    &lt;p class&#x3D;&quot;card-text&quot;&gt;&#123;&#123;i.login&#125;&#125;的Github&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;\n                    &lt;a href&#x3D;&quot;&#123;&#123;i.html_url&#125;&#125;&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;btn btn-primary&quot;&gt;Github&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;\n                &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n            &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n            &lt;br&gt;\n        &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n        &#123;% endfor %&#125;\n    &lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;\n&#123;% endblock %&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/62/77/lD7AgzbQ_o.png\"></p>\n<!--stackedit_data:\neyJoaXN0b3J5IjpbLTE3ODMwNjYxNjhdfQ==\n-->","feature":true,"text":"將API資料顯示到網站 Github API 1. 把API資訊導入 首先我們先從pizzawu中的 view.py，我們要加入API的資訊 from django.shortcuts import render # Create your views here. def hom...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Python.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"django","slug":"django","count":6,"path":"api/tags/django.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B0%87API%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%88%B0%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">將API資料顯示到網站</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E6%8A%8AAPI%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 把API資訊導入</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%A5%E5%BE%8C%E8%A6%81%E5%86%8DHTML%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 導入後要再HTML顯示</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E7%94%A8Bootstrap%E7%BE%8E%E5%8C%96\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 用Bootstrap美化</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%95%B4%E7%90%86%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8Bjson\"><span class=\"toc-text\">整理一下json</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0Bootstrap\"><span class=\"toc-text\">增加Bootstrap</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Cabie Wu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://sites.google.com/site/jiayulpy/_/rsrc/1466150305751/1235/2.jpg","